<li><a href="http://www.env.go.jp/en/chemi/hs/minamata2002/" class="external text" title="http://www.env.go.jp/en/chemi/hs/minamata2002/" rel="nofollow">"Minamata Disease: The History and Measures"</a>, The <a href="/wiki/Ministry_of_the_Environment_(Japan)" title="Ministry of the Environment (Japan)">Ministry of the Environment</a>, (2002), retrieved <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2007-01-17"><a href="/wiki/January_17" title="January 17">17 January</a> <a href="/wiki/2007" title="2007">2007</a></span></li>
