<li>George, S. Timothy. (2001). <i>Minamata: Pollution and the Struggle for Democracy in Postwar Japan</i>. Harvard University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0674007859" class="internal">ISBN 0-674-00785-9</a></li>
<li>Ui, Jun. (1992). <i><a href="http://www.unu.edu/unupress/unupbooks/uu35ie/uu35ie00.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.unu.edu/unupress/unupbooks/uu35ie/uu35ie00.htm" rel="nofollow">Industrial Pollution in Japan</a></i>. United Nations University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9280805487" class="internal">ISBN 92-808-0548-7</a>. Chapter 4, section IV</li>
